==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: -ed
<hw>-ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>The termination of the past participle
of regular, or weak, verbs; also, of analogous participial adjectives
from nouns; <as>as, pigment<ex>ed</ex>;
talent<ex>ed</ex>.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Edacious</ent>⟦br⟧
